  "prompt": "What is the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai?",
  "response": "As of 2023, the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai ranges between AED 120,000 to AED 250,000 per year, depending on factors such as:\n\n1. Experience level\n- Entry-level: AED 90,000 - 150,000\n- Mid-level: AED 150,000 - 220,000\n- Senior-level: AED 220,000 - 350,000\n\n2. Specific IT specialization\n- Cybersecurity consultants\n- Cloud computing consultants\n- Network infrastructure consultants\n- Digital transformation consultants\n\n3. Company size and reputation\n4. Individual qualifications and certifications\n\nPlease note that these figures are approximate and can vary based on current market conditions and individual circumstances. Actual salaries may differ, and it's recommended to consult current job market reports or recruitment agencies for the most up-to-date information.",
